variable.comment: Character variable Blank = Field not filled in. Non-blank = Field filled in.

variable.name: Cystatin_C
variable.comment: The lower detectable limit for CYSTATIN_C is 2480 pg/mL and the upper detectable limit is 2680000 pg/mL. CYSTATIN_C values below or above these limits were set to the lower or upper detectable limit respectively. Use CYSTATIN_C_I to see what records are below and above these limits. CYSTATIN_C values were set to unknown if CYSTATIN_C_CV was greater than or equal to 23.8 for Offspring (IDTYPE = 1) or 22.3 for Gen 3 (IDTYPE = 3).
